PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the use by the Province of ALBERTA of its statutory powers to acquire a right-of-way over some 22.59 hectares of SWAN RIVER INDIAN RESERVE NO. 150E, for the purposes of the existing roadway and public utilities located thereon, and (b) authorizing the transfer of those lands to the Province, in lieu of exercising their powers.
